title: Derrick Van Orden Wins Wisconsin House Seat
description: Derrick Van Orden, a Navy SEAL who rallied at the Capitol on Jan. 6, 2021, beat Brad Pfaff, a Democratic state senator, flipping a House seat in rural Wisconsin.
dc:creator: Catie Edmondson
media:description: Derrick Van Orden, a retired Navy SEAL who rallied at the Capitol on Jan. 6, 2021, ran against a Democratic state senator, Brad Pfaff, for a House seat in rural Wisconsin.
